  </m:mfrac>
  <m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.3em"/><m:mtext>kW</m:mtext>
 </m:mrow>
</m:math> . Considering that a car engine delivers about 100 kW of power, this is not bad for a little capacitor!</para>
</commentary>
