</para>-->
<para id="fs-id1164567882230">You insert a dielectric into an air-filled capacitor. How does this affect the energy stored in the capacitor?</para>
<list id="fs-id1164567216928" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>Energy stored in the capacitor will remain same.</item>
<item>Energy stored in the capacitor will decrease.</item>
<item>Energy stored in the capacitor will increase.</item>
<item>Energy stored in the capacitor will increase first, and then it will decrease.</item></list>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="eip-id1166849845850" class="os-exercise">
<problem id="eip-id1166849622881">
